rows.label: qst701109_msg0001
rows.name:
The master helped me out a lot in the
past. He picked me up when I was a
wreck from all my reckless behavior.

rows.label: qst701109_msg0002
rows.name:
He'd get angry and worry about me straight
on. Even though there was no profit in it,
he was the only adult who was kind to me.

rows.label: qst701109_msg0003
rows.name:
I decided back then that if the
master was in trouble, no matter
what, I would be the one to help him.

rows.label: qst701109_msg0004
rows.name:
So I came prepared this time, but I was relieved
it was just about Wotta. He's the type who
can't do anything bad even if he tried.

rows.label: qst701109_msg0005
rows.name:
It makes him an easy target... Ah,
don't tell the master I said that!?
